Assignment 1:
Create a class called Transition which has two methods of Transition 
1) ManualTransition 
2) AutomaticTransition 

Use Transition class as a parent class for child classes to inherit from it and create Car and MotorCycle as child classes 
and override the methods of manualTransition and automaticTransition 
in main function use a pointer of Transition that can point to each of the child classes objects and display the transition method
